languages.text: "В чем дело? Я правда пугаю вас настолько, что даже глаз не поднять?" {n}Каллигос раздраженно рычит.{/n} "Где этот нелепый псайкер? Эй, старик! Уж ты то знаешь, как почтить словом своего господина!"

languages.text: "What's the matter? Am I truly so terrifying that you cannot even look at me?" {n}Calligos growls in exasperation.{/n} "Where is that ridiculous psyker? At least he knows how to honour his master with his words. Old man!"

traits.locale_text: «¿Qué pasa? ¿Tanto miedo os doy que ni siquiera os atrevéis a mirarme?». {n}Calligos ruge de frustración.{/n} «¿Dónde está ese ridículo psíquico? ¡Eh, viejo! ¡Demuestra que tú sí sabes honrar a tu amo con tu palabrería!».

languages.text: “都怎么了？我真的这么可怕，你们看都不敢看我一眼吗？”{n}卡里戈斯恼怒地咆哮着。{/n}“那个满嘴胡话的灵能者在哪里？他肯定知道怎么恭维他的主人！喂，老家伙！”
languages.original_text: "What's the matter? Am I truly so terrifying that you cannot even look at me?" {n}Calligos growls in exasperation.{/n} "Where is that ridiculous psyker? At least he knows how to honour his master with his words. Old man!"

traits.locale_text: “都怎么了？我真的这么吓人，你们都不敢看我一眼吗？”{n}卡里戈斯沮丧地咆哮着。{/n}“那个满嘴胡话的灵能者在哪里？喂，老家伙！你肯定知道怎么恭维你的主人吧！”

languages.text: « Qu'y a-t-il ? Suis-je donc si terrifiant que vous n'osez même plus me regarder ? {n}grogne Calligos avec exaspération.{/n} Où est ce psyker ridicule ? Lui au moins, il sait quoi dire pour honorer son maître ! Vieillard ! »
languages.original_text: "What's the matter? Am I truly so terrifying that you cannot even look at me?" {n}Calligos growls in exasperation.{/n} "Where is that ridiculous psyker? At least he knows how to honour his master with his words. Old man!"

traits.locale_text: « Qu'y a-t-il ? Suis-je terrifiant au point que vous n'osez même plus me regarder ? {n}demande Calligos en grondant de frustration.{/n} Où est ce psyker ridicule ? Vieillard ! Toi, tu sais certainement quoi dire pour honorer ton maître ! »

languages.text: 「どうしたんだ？俺を見ることさえできないほどに怖いのか？」{n}カリゴスは不満げに唸る。{/n}「このバカな異能者はどこだ？あいつは少なくとも言葉で主人を敬う方法を知っているだろう。おい、老いぼれ！」
languages.original_text: "What's the matter? Am I truly so terrifying that you cannot even look at me?" {n}Calligos growls in exasperation.{/n} "Where is that ridiculous psyker? At least he knows how to honour his master with his words. Old man!"

traits.locale_text: 「どうしたんだ？俺を見ることさえできないほどに怖いのか？」{n}カリゴスは不満げに唸る。{/n}「このバカな異能者はどこだ？あいつは少なくとも言葉で主人を敬う方法を知っているだろう。おい、老いぼれ！」

languages.text: "Was ist denn? Bin ich wirklich so furchterregend, dass Ihr mich nicht einmal ansehen könnt?" {n}Calligos knurrt aufgebracht.{/n} "Wo ist dieser lächerliche Psioniker? Er weißt zumindest, wie man seinen Meister mit seinen Worten ehrt. Alter Mann!"
languages.original_text: "What's the matter? Am I truly so terrifying that you cannot even look at me?" {n}Calligos growls in exasperation.{/n} "Where is that ridiculous psyker? At least he knows how to honour his master with his words. Old man!"

traits.locale_text: "Was ist denn? Bin ich so furchterregend, dass Ihr mich nicht einmal ansehen könnt?" {n}Calligos schreit seinen Frust heraus.{/n} "Wer ist dieser lächerliche Psioniker? Hey, alter Mann! Ihr wisst doch bestimmt, wie Ihr Euren Meister mit Euren Worten ehren müsst!"

languages.text: "Sorun ne? Gerçekten o kadar korkunç biri miyim ki bana bakamıyorsunuz?" {n}Calligos, hiddetle homurdanıyor.{/n} "Şu komik tipli ruhsezer nerede? En azından o, sözleriyle efendisini onurlandırmayı biliyor. İhtiyar adam!"
